/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 712 Tm
(- Maku Cafe is a role-based cafe operations system for cashier ordering, manager oversight,) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 698 Tm
(  menu availability control, and kitchen order fulfillment.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 680 Tm
(- Cashiers create customer orders from the active product menu. Managers monitor transactions,) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 666 Tm
(  staff accounts, daily metrics, and product availability. Kitchen staff receive pending) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 652 Tm
(  receipts and mark them complete after preparation.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 634 Tm
(- The system is implemented as an Express.js application serving static HTML, CSS, and) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 620 Tm
(  JavaScript screens backed by a MySQL database. Authentication uses server-side sessions and) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 606 Tm
(  role-based page guards.) Tj
/F2 15 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 580 Tm
(Objectives) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 558 Tm
(- Provide a clear point-of-sale workflow for cashiers, including product selection,) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 544 Tm
(  configurable options, checkout, held orders, notes, and payment mode selection.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 526 Tm
(- Keep cashier menus accurate by hiding unavailable products and allowing managers to toggle) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 512 Tm
(  menu availability without code changes.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 494 Tm
(- Track operational activity through manager-facing metrics, audit logs, staff profile) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 480 Tm
(  controls, and daily revenue/order summaries.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 462 Tm
