1 0 0 1 54 390 Tm
(System Architecture) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 368 Tm
(- Client layer: Static UI pages under ui/models. Key screens include login.html, cashier.html,) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 354 Tm
(  manager.html, profile.html, and kitchen.html. Each screen has paired CSS and JavaScript for) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 340 Tm
(  page behavior.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 322 Tm
(- Server layer: Express.js in server/index.js. The server mounts API route groups for) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 308 Tm
(  authentication, products, orders, and manager operations. It also serves protected pages) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 294 Tm
(  through pageAuth middleware.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 276 Tm
(- Authentication: /api/login validates bcrypt password hashes, checks account status, creates) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 262 Tm
(  a user session, and stores role information in req.session.user. /api/logout closes the) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 248 Tm
(  tracked session.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 230 Tm
(- Product/menu flow: /api/products returns only available products to cashiers.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 216 Tm
(  /api/manager/products returns all products for manager availability control. Product options) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 202 Tm
(  are loaded through /api/products/:id/options.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 184 Tm
(- Order flow: cashier checkout creates a pending order with order_items and order_item_addons.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 170 Tm
(  The kitchen board fetches pending orders from /api/kitchen/orders and completes them through) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 156 Tm
(  /api/kitchen/orders/:id/complete. Completion sets status to completed, completed_at, and) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 142 Tm
(  completed_by.) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 124 Tm
(- Manager flow: manager dashboard aggregates orders, items sold, daily revenue, registration) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 110 Tm
(  requests, staff profiles, and audit rows. Audit rows include listed, completed, voided,) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 96 Tm
(  refunded, and session clock events.) Tj
